<i>noun</i>: 서약 [서ː약], 맹세 [맹세], 맹서 [맹서] <i>verb</i>: 서약하다 [서ː야카다], 맹세하다 [맹세하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>서약 [서ː약]</dt><br>
<dd>vow; oath; pledge</dd><br>
<dd>맹세하고 약속함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of making a vow to keep a promise.</dd><br>
<dt>맹세 [맹세]</dt><br>
<dd>vow</dd><br>
<dd>굳게 다짐하거나 약속함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of making a firm commitment or promise.</dd><br>
<dt>맹서 [맹서]</dt><br>
<dd>pledge; oath; vow</dd><br>
<dd>굳게 다짐하거나 약속함.</dd><br>
<dd>A firm commitment or promise.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>서약하다 [서ː야카다]</dt><br>
<dd>vow; pledge</dd><br>
<dd>맹세하고 약속하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make a vow to keep a promise.</dd><br>
<dt>맹세하다 [맹세하다]</dt><br>
<dd>vow</dd><br>
<dd>굳게 다짐하거나 약속하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make a firm commitment or promise.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>